data.description: Nestled on a generous half-acre plot, this 2700 square foot haven redefines relaxation living with a perfect blend modern upgrades and serene surroundings. Step into a world of comfort and style as you explore the features that make this residence truly exceptional. As you approach the property, your gaze is immediately drawn to the well-maintained exterior, crowned by a brand-new roof installed in 2017. This recent addition not only enhances the home's curb appeal but also ensures lasting durability and protection for years to come. The reassurance of a solid roof sets the tone for the quality that awaits within.The heart of this home lies in its completely renovated kitchen, a masterpiece unveiled in 2017. Imagine stepping into a culinary haven where every detail has been carefully curated for both aesthetics and functionality. Gleaming countertops, state-of-the-art appliances, and ample space come together to create a kitchen that is as beautiful as it is practical. Whether you're an aspiring chef or simply love to gather with family and friends, this kitchen is designed to elevate your culinary experience. As you move through the home, you'll appreciate the thoughtful upgrades that extend beyond the kitchen. The HVAC was replaced in 2023, ensuring efficiency and reliability. A new water heater installed in 2023 adds another layer of convenience to this residence. Enjoy the luxury of a reliable and energy-efficient water heating system, providing a seamless supply of hot water for your daily needs.Beyond the walls of the house lies a captivating feature - a tranquil lake that graces the backyard. Imagine waking up to the soothing sounds of nature, enjoying a cup in your sunroom as you gaze upon the serene waters. This private oasis not only enhances the aesthetic appeal of the property but also offers a peaceful retreat right outside your door. Discover the perfect union of elegance and relaxation and set up a showing today!!
